<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>Funeral</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hatak pilbʋsha fehna hosh,
 Himak hitak oka,
 Yaha̱ya bieka hoch,
 Il itafamʋshke.

[V2]
 Ai illit pi̱ kʋnia hosh
 Il anukfihinlit,
 Chu̱kʋsh nukha̱klo biekʋt,
 E taloho̱wʋshke.

[V3]
 Hatak yoshoba pia kʋt,
 Nana ilbʋsha ka
 E pihi̱sa he tuk okʋt,
 Pim ʋlhpiesʋshke.

[V4]
 Ahnit, himak nitak oka,
 Chisʋs e hoyo kʋt,
 Pi̱ nukha̱klokbano, ahnit,
 Il im asilhhʋshke.

[V5]
 Pishno kia ik pillo hosh
 Il anta chi̱ keyu;
 Illi pim ʋlhta̱yak okʋt,
 Ik pihinlo ka wa.

[V6]
 Illi achukma pulla ka
 Pim ʋlhtaha tuk osh
 Pillikmʋt, ʋba yakni a̱
 Eho pihi̱sashke.
 7 Chisʋs pi Okchalinchi ma!
 Ish pi̱ nukha̱klo cha,
 Chim anukfila hokʋno
 Ish pima pullashke.</lyrics>
<title>Hatak pilbʋsha fehna hosh ƲIT113</title>
<time_sig>C.M. (8.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<hymn_number>113</hymn_number>
</song>